Seeker slsk client

This repository contains official releases of the Seeker soulseek client from https://github.com/jackBonadies/SeekerAndroid

Currently it serves 1 apps. To add it to your F-Droid client, scan the QR code (click it to enlarge) or use this URL:

https://raw.githubusercontent.com/jackBonadies/SeekerAndroid/fdroid/fdroid/repo
